gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Done extraordinary thing, then taken by great king;
Pulled out a girl from Kshatriya clan, sitting every day in assumption.

Wali Gajra Baandi Be Haath, Aape Prasadi Padhaarya Naath;
Tehe Har Ne Gajra Jeh, Ditha Prakat Sahu Jene Teh.

Build a wall of thorns with two hands, I won't follow you; 
That very defeat will be yours, know this, and don't forget.
